<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM14.1">
<l>paṭṭi mēyntōr kārēṟu palatē vaṟkōr kīḻkkaṉṟāy</l>
<l>iṭṭī ṟiṭṭu viḷaiyāṭi yiṅkē pōtak kaṇṭīrē</l>
<l>iṭṭamāṉa pacukkaḷai yiṉitu maṟittu nīrūṭṭi</l>
<l>viṭṭuk koṇṭu viḷaiyāṭa viruntā vaṉattē kaṇṭōmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Did you see the unique Black Cloud, Baladeva’s younger calf[-like brother],</l>
<l>Passing by loitering around and playing arrogantly?</l>
<l>We saw Him play in Bṛndāvana sweetly detaining the favourite cows,</l>
<l>feeding [them] water, and letting [them graze]!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
